name: Changing Woman (Asdzáá Nádlééhé)
shortLoreBlurb: Personification of life’s cycles who renews the world and grants hózhó (beauty/balance).
overlapsLinks: Manannán mac Lir (Celtic), Naga (India/SE Asia), Njord (Norse), Poseidon (Greek), Tangaroa (Polynesia)
description: Personification of life’s cycles who renews the world and grants hózhó (beauty/balance).
